		dependencies: ["000000000000301E"]
		title: "Dressed to the Bone"
		icon: {id: "kubejs:boneanner_chestplate", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Bone and banana — an unlikely pair, but Kieransmama has never been conventional. Craft the Boneanner Chestplate, Leggings, and Boots to complete the set. What you lack in style you will more than make up for in Projectile Protection.", "Once the set is complete, three paths will open. Each one defines what kind of warrior you are — Plate for raw defense, Leather for agility, Cloth for arcane power. Choose one path only. Apply the modifiers to all three pieces. There is no going back."]
