		title: "The Plate Path"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/force_soul_tag_armor_stat", Count: 1b}
		description: ["You have chosen the Plate Path. Your Boneanner armor will become heavy plate — built to absorb punishment and hold the line. Use each of the three Force Soul Tag: Armor modifiers on your Chestplate, Leggings, and Boots to lock in the plate archetype across the full set. Do not complete the other paths."]
