		title: "The Leather Path"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/force_soul_tag_dodge_stat", Count: 1b}
		description: ["You have chosen the Leather Path. Your Boneanner armor will become supple leather — built for those who survive by not being where the blade lands. Use each of the three Force Soul Tag: Dodge modifiers on your Chestplate, Leggings, and Boots to lock in the leather archetype across the full set. Do not complete the other paths."]
