		description: ["You have chosen the Cloth Path. Your Boneanner armor will become woven cloth — built for those who answer steel with something far less forgiving. Use each of the three Force Soul Tag: Magic Shield modifiers on your Chestplate, Leggings, and Boots to lock in the cloth archetype across the full set. Do not complete the other paths."]
